                            <comment id="13145193" author="dvryaboy" created="Mon, 7 Nov 2011 03:19:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Daniel, I am getting some odd errors trying to use bin/pig with the default version of hadoop that&apos;s bundled (20.2). Stack trace below. Is this related?&lt;/p&gt;

